title: Westlife - Greatest Hits [2011] DVD9
description: Westlife - Greatest Hits [2011] DVD9 Greatest Hits is the second greatest hits album and final release by Irish boy band Westlife. It was released on 18 November 2011 by RCA Records and Sony Music following Unbreakable: The Greatest Hits Volume 1 (2002). The compilation was released in two different formats, a standard edition containing the album's eighteen tracks, and a deluxe edition featuring numerous other singles of the band's discography, as well as this DVD containing almost all of the the Irish quartet's videos that were released between 1999 and 2010.l Country: United Kingdom, Ireland Genre: Pop Duration: 2:14 Year of manufacture: 2011.
